						<div class="postbody">If you have no need for video out (although I don't know why you wouldn't need it), you can in fact use the PPU address bus to control peripheral devices, without adding much extra logic to control them.<br /><br />You can use the audio out to generate square waves of varying duty and frequency, although it is important to know that these are analog signals so you should connect to something that is using such a signal (normally, it is the speaker in a TV set).<br /><br />What is it that you are trying to make anyways?</div>

					
